    &w&para <b>Exercise 4. Complete each sentence using words from you vocabulary list</b>
    </p>
    <ol>
        <li>
            Þere has been an emergency! We need you here <u>&emsp\;anon&emsp\;</u>!
        </li>
        <li>
            You said we could choose a topic, but I cannot þink of <u>&emsp\;aught&emsp\;</u> to write about.
        </li>
        <li>
            Would you please come <u>&emsp\;hiþer&emsp\;</u>, I need to talk to you.
        </li>
        <li>
            Your <u>&emsp\;alacrity&emsp\;</u> for þe task shows a real enþusiasm. I’m glad to see it!
        </li>
        <li>
            If you work hard and show your abilities, it might aid in your <u>&emsp\;preferment&emsp\;</u> at work.
        </li>
        <li>
