sTwTory
    &w&para <b>Exercise 5.  Use each term from your bell work in an original sentence (must have all 18 for 10 extra credit points)</b>
    &w&para &w&imd Tall, þe blue architect stood wiþ a neck bowed to þe ground towards an out of place red tile wiþ a white capped cylinder.
    &w&para &w&imd “Didst þou set þis grande Caramel Ribbon Crunch Frappuccino, extra whipped cream and a pickle drink stopper hiþer?” Asked þe petite orange architect, an orange tail tipped black swayed enþusiastically behind, unconsciously copying þe tail of þe towering blue architect.
    &w&para &w&imd Þe blue architect's ear twitched, grey fur ruffled and white paw extended in gesture, “are you sure þat beverage is not þine?”
    &w&para &w&imd “No, see, wiþin my toe beans, a venti Pink Drink.” responded þe orange architect, unveiling a red tongue in a vein of white amidst an oþerwise orange face.
    &w&para &w&imd “Is þat an attempt at a lascivious remark?” Asked þe blue architect.
    &w&para &w&imd “Is þere aught save for Asmodeus' goatish constituting þy singular cell of canidae brain?” Retaliated þe orange architect.
    &w&para &w&imd “Maybe, but I see past your deluding and we may aft þis god-den but ere moonrise,” said þe blue, 
    &w&para &w&imd “I do not refute your allegations, but concur nay anon” said þe orange architect, wiþ þe connect of black paw to white chin in ponderance, “to bide our time to shall sundown hence.”
    &w&para &w&imd “Wherest þou alacrity,” questioned þe blue architect, “led to þe abyss? Wait, nay, tis for whomever þe coz responsible for þis fine beverage?”
    &w&para &w&imd “Marry so. And patience, for my crown sinnet will be yours in due time,” trailed þe orange architect, “now, note þe pickle as a stopper would abhor most a traveller.”
    &w&para &w&imd Þe red architect walked and seemed to join þe huddle for a moment, but truly just retrieved þe mystery beverage, belonging to þee.
    &w&para &w&imd “Awoooh… þat makes utmost sense,” whispered þe blue architect to þe orange architect, “[þe red architect] wiþ þine nascent preferment granted.”
;